WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:01.267 --> 00:00:03.667
&gt;&gt; To add an event gadget
to your website,

00:00:03.667 --> 00:00:06.167
go to google.com/friendconnect.

00:00:06.167 --> 00:00:08.400
Click on social gadgets

00:00:08.400 --> 00:00:13.801
and then event gadget.

00:00:13.801 --> 00:00:17.400
Enter an event title
and description.

00:00:17.400 --> 00:00:21.267
Set the date and time,

00:00:21.267 --> 00:00:26.100
and then the time zone.

00:00:26.100 --> 00:00:29.033
Enter the location

00:00:29.033 --> 00:00:34.234
and a URL to an image
or video.

00:00:34.234 --> 00:00:37.367
Then click generate code,

00:00:37.367 --> 00:00:42.234
and copy the snippet
into the body of your HTML.

00:00:42.234 --> 00:00:43.901
With the event gadget,

00:00:43.901 --> 00:00:47.467
visitors can see a map,

00:00:47.467 --> 00:00:51.968
indicate if they're coming,

00:00:51.968 --> 00:00:54.701
and see who else
is attending.

00:00:54.701 --> 00:00:56.133
They can even add the event

00:00:56.133 --> 00:00:59.267
to their Google calendar
with just a click.

00:00:59.267 --> 00:01:04.300
Go to google.com/friendconnect
to get started.

